instance-variables.MessageIF: [A familiar voice] Welcome to the village.
Someone will make a great meal out of these.
From a distance, it looks like there's writing on it, but now you realise these are just grey squares.
I wonder where they got these from. I haven't seen a forest or anything.
I think it's locked. Why isn't anyone ever home in these RPGs?
You're not thinking about stealing them, are you?
Too bad you're allergic to that.
Where did they go after they got out of that boat?
Tip: things that you can examine will show an icon when you hover over them. That tree sure looks interesting.
